Package: qrreader
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: QR/barcode serial reader (PyInstaller binary)
 Standalone qrreader: serial scanner to clipboard paste.
 Configure port in /etc/qrreader/port.
 Enable: systemctl --user enable --now qrreader.service
